meta_info.name: REVISION_HISTORY
meta_info.description: Purpose Defines the notion of a revision history of audit items, each associated with the version for which that audit was committed. The list is in most-recent-first order.

functions.name: most_recent_version
functions.meaning: The version id of the most recent item, as a String.

functions.name: most_recent_version_time_committed
functions.meaning: The commit date/time of the most recent item, as a String.

attributes.name: items
attributes.description: The items in this history in most-recent-last order.
